overall deposit fire-rate: control=100.0%  cf=100.0%
decision points: control=645  cf=199

READ: if within-bin fire-rates (rate gap) are ~0 while the bin POPULATIONS shift
poorward in cf, the floor grounds by G1 (trajectory) alone -- zero regime detection.
That means norm_contingency measures mechanical divergence, and genuine grounding (G2)
needs a money-matched metric the program hasn't been scoring.
